snippet.title: One S'More - Gameplay Trailer [02]
snippet.description:
👾 Play One S‘More for free on Steam: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2452930/One_SMore/

One S'More is a wholesome puzzle game that will melt your brain and your heart. 🧠

Watch your mind crumble as you break apart islands and rearrange entire levels to help your little marshmallow friend get squished between two chocolate cookies. 🍪

💬 Join the Discord Server: 
 https://discord.com/invite/dBJ7XgBtPM

🎶 Musik:
Once In Paris von Pumpupthemind
https://pixabay.com/music/beats-once-in-paris-168895/

#cozygaming #gamedev #gaming #puzzlegame
